schedule.appointment.patient

Class Patient

  • java.lang.Object
    • schedule.appointment.patient.Patient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Patient>

    public class Patient
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Patient>
    The Patient class creates necessary information for a patient object. Gives the patient object their first and last name as well as their date-of-birth. Patient objects can compare to one another to see if they are the same patient or not.
